BIBREF0.title: Experimental (thick dashed line) and calculated (thin continuous line) ESR spectra of 5PC in MLVs of DMPC/DMPG/Chol=40/30/30 at pH 7 and 37 o C are supeerimposed. The upper one is the spectrum from the vesicles without TM-wt, while the lower one from the vesicles containing TM-wt with molar ratio TM-wt/lipids = 1/75. The outer peak separation of the two spectra is 54.8 G and 55.8 G, respectively. A part of the high field peak of the spectra is magnified in the inserted box. An inflection in the lower spectrum is marked by an arrow
